<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，小美人鱼十五岁的生日到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天你终于能看见地上世界了。”奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好兴奋！”小美人鱼大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我等这一天等了好久了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼把一个白百合编成的花环，戴在小美人鱼的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，在她的尾巴上挂上了象征着王族的四个牡蛎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，好疼！”小美人鱼大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是成为十五岁的一个小牺牲。”奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼也承认牡蛎看起来很美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她渴望到地上世界的冒险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿，奶奶。”小美人鱼恳求说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快去吧，宝贝。”奶奶说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但别呆太久了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>记住，你的家在这里，在海底。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼急忙着拥抱了奶奶，说了声再见，就游走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当小美人鱼到达海面时，太阳刚落山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看见天空从蓝色变成了粉色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了夜晚，天空变成了深紫色，星光闪闪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，月亮光照到了海面上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地上世界好美啊！”小美人鱼大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>远远地，小美人鱼看见一艘船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她游近了一点，看见船停在水里一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>音乐响着，她看见了明亮、彩色的光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船员们在船的甲板上走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们用两条腿走路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是人类？”她说，“好奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她兴奋地一直游到船边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从外向里面看，里面有更多的人在唱歌、跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都穿着漂亮的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看起来是个派对！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼仔细地看着每个人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她注意到了一个年轻人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，他好帅。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当所有人都往甲板上走时，她目不转睛地看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们记得十六年前您出生时的样子，王子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个头上戴着蓝色羽毛的女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个王子！”小美人鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个客人说：“你有善良的心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以后，您会成为一位伟大的国王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝您每年都像今年这么幸福！”一个男人举杯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“生日快乐，王子！”人群一起欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个人都爱他。”小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一定很棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>烟花冲上天空，化作数千个小火花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水面反射出火花，整个大海闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊！”小美人鱼从来没见过这样的情景。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吓得飞快地游到了水底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她从水底看上去，很快就不再害怕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天上有好多闪闪发光的火花！”她兴奋地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子跟客人拥抱、握手，说：“谢谢你们为我庆祝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼游到了海面上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子是所有人类中最帅的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跟她花园的雕像一样帅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，很快，音乐就停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五颜六色的灯也灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们帮忙！”王子对他的船员们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个派对太棒了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，王子和他的客人们走到甲板下去睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼不想离开船，还有英俊的王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为她对王子一见钟情了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>